{"type": "article", "id": 55106, "title": "一款打火机的现代美学，来自金属的质感｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-07-10T23:16:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 37360, "name": "Socio Design"}, {"id": 15115, "name": "QWSTION"}, {"id": 51736, "name": "Femme Atelier"}, {"id": 51737, "name": "Humanhome"}, {"id": 51738, "name": "Elisa Otañez"}, {"id": 51739, "name": "Marco Zagaria"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 160, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180711071605JUA8sig4q93ER0x5.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #141414; -webkit-text-stroke: #141414} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #111111; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #111111} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s8 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Egloo by Marco Zagaria</h3><p>Egloo 是一款室内加热器，出自设计师 Marco Zagaria 之手。它的独特之处在于其采用蜡烛发热，提供了便宜又环保的热能，解决冬天一开空调，电表数字蹭蹭往上跳的难题。</p><p>这是一款不需要插电的陶瓷小暖炉，只需点上四根小蜡烛，它号称能在10分钟的时间内将一间小屋子的温度提高 10 度。Egloo 官网写道：“当前人们在供暖方面的用电量越来越大，Egloo 小暖炉的创意正来自于这种背景下，它的供暖方式更便宜、更环保，它的陶瓷外壳能够将蜡烛的热量缓慢向外辐射，即便蜡烛灭了之后还能保持一段时间的温度。”</p><p>目前，它在众筹网站 Kickstarter 上的众筹价格为 50 欧元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1018374213/egloo-candle-powered-heater\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807102211525SoDpevTcuFOzn0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221152vwiFCS9WjagYu7Q1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221152odW6nCrfGAyl1mhD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221152BtFOc9GxlipgNz0P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221152jtDCyHTkv5b8PZBo.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221152Yy14UA9V5zJ3pjfB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.619048\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221153xUpw03q5sE8ihRek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>ODIS Sconce by Humanhome</h3><p>洛杉矶 Human Home 设计工作室设计出的灯具系列，很符合清爽、简约的当代家居风格。他们的代表作，是将以往让人感觉笨重的落地灯，结合软性材质与极简线条，将灯具变得轻盈，让观者有一种漂浮在墙壁上的错觉，整体看起来清爽又别具特色。</p><p>比如最新推出的 ODIS SCONCE 系列，手工制作，结合了极简主义风格和工业风，由圆形钢制框架和美国黑胡桃木组合构成，球形灯泡镶嵌于中心位置。整体灯具采用插入式设计，允许用户将其安装在相对靠近插座的任何位置，相对较为灵活。售价 250 美元，<a href=\"https://humanhome.co/products/odis-sconce\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245ItY3mMAxUnDTvfsr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245iUQM6vFOYl4kImZV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245UJhB3HXoN0emgyac.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245S6UnsmLHtaGBoJW8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245lVSGMXU8YdhvrKiN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221245UL0AGyIMqONa9CZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221246N23L9aI1CgOvKrt5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><p>图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/humanhome-launches-a-new-plug-in-light-called-the-odis-sconce/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></p></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Framemust Collection by Femme Atelier</h3><p>设计师 Mew Kamonwan 和 Lalita Kitchachanchaikul 最近在曼谷创立了工作室 Femme Atelier，试图实验和重新构想日常物品。最新推出的 Framemust 系列，包括两张桌子和两个凳子，以传统的门框和窗框为灵感，用挤压铝型材制成，用渐变色彩作为饰面，搭配经过粉末涂层处理的铝制部件，创造出一组色彩丰富多样的作品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221332SJFKacU6f4hGWjEs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221332tC8y1LHY4rDRbMe6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221332SIADN53tVwMjqGQE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.078000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221333eodxnVqYU1fp5RZW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807102213337gAMbHxqs5P980K1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.783000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221333W2lCycOSxwe0kEfF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221333Jz9RfQSvZHbcrGIw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.515000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/65669637/Framemust\" rel=\"nofollow\">Behance</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Yellow Spot by Elisa Otañez</h3><p>埃因霍温设计学院的毕业生 Elisa Otañez 创造了一个黄色的移动卫生间，用实际行动抗议荷兰缺乏为女性服务的公共设施的现状。来自墨西哥的 Elisa Otañez 发现，荷兰很多城市都有不少公共小便池，但对于女性友好的卫生间很少。</p><p>她希望找到一种有效的解决方案，Yellow Spot 由三个部分组成，带有滑轮的亮黄色框架，保证隐私的帆布板以及小型黄色马桶。彩绘框架由直管状钢管制成，并用螺栓连接，产生类似于脚手架的效果。</p><p>黄色帆布板上标有“free toilet”和 “occupied by women”的标语，是醒目的黑色字样。帆布的前面板用夹子固定，可以轻松打开和关闭。关于女性可用公共厕所数量的事实印在里面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221418a129GqJtpzUKvCie.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.558799\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221418wbqFUAcI8t9HmoeL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.557530\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221418bc5SIO4NemqaALx6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675973\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018071022141989id2J5orpnPXWjO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221419EFCpL0xdRyKz7YhQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.559645\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/07/09/yellow-spot-design-academy-eindhoven-portable-protest-toilet-elisa-otanez/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>SMALL PACK Raw Blend Leather Canvas by QWSTION</h3><p>创立于 2008 年的苏黎世包袋品牌 <a href=\"http://www.qwstion.com/en/home/\" rel=\"nofollow\">QWSTION</a> ， 认同设计大师 Mies van der Rohe 的“少即是多”理念，主张兼具时尚感和功能性的包袋，应该是简约而不浮夸的。</p><p>最近，它们为品牌标志性的包袋 Simple Pack 推出了新版本 Small Pack，虽然尺寸较之原版变得更小，但功能性得以保留。除了易于拿取的外部口袋和两个拉链式外口袋，适合收纳较小的物品，内部带衬垫的隔层可以收纳 13 英寸电脑。可调节背包带和顶部手柄完善了整体紧凑的设计。售价 230 美元，<a href=\"https://www.qwstion.com/us/bags/small-pack-raw-blend-leather-canvas.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221511bgSW1riI9soZV5hT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221511xgUz9HQknZIE1l0D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221511utZoDP9LqaIYNWH2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.200000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221512EqzfrpnlXh8iJtP1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221514xsnbFSHrjaCz3Iwt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>KNNOX Lighter by Socio Design</h3><p>KNNOX 打火机是一款兼具了现代美学和精密手工工艺的设计。英国 Socio Design 团队希望能够挑战典型打火机的外形特征，重构其外形。设计师选择实心黄铜作为主要材料，醒目的颜色和厚重的质地，为的是强调精确的细节。随着时间的推移，KNNOX 打火机还会在每日的磨损中附着上斑驳的时间痕迹，呈现出老化的美感。耐用性成为 KNNOX 体验中不可或缺的一部分。</p><p>值得一提的是，打火机的每个部件都是单独包装的，买回去后由使用者自行组装。每个打火机都配有自己的高品质灯芯，燧石和不锈钢六角工具。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221602Bk1K9R7ToIOchGf4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221602bQcNY9Dnqr1i2s8J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221602RzUp51KW3t6juFw2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201807102216022wmplbX4onOBUYsc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221602LUGujdzTJPyN69B5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221602eh0tbkqzAUi5Jv9X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221603A29eUubK1Hqc0lCr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180710221603l7brSi1cg2WDTvJm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://minimalissimo.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">minimalissimo.com</a></figcaption></figure></div>"}